Sensors
accelerometer acceleration m/s^2
gyro rad/s (convert from deg/s)
(x, y, z for both) + other parameters if necessary
- Outputs acceleration & gyro vectors
Clock included for timestamp

magnometer microtesla (mu T)
Input mag vector (x, y, z), calibration
Output mag vector & timestamp if needed
- Finds absolute yaw (heading) corrects altitude

GPS/GNSS reciever position m/s (ENU/NED convert)
Input GNSS data stream, antenna status, configuration
Output (x,y,z lat/long), velocity, fix status & timestamp

PPS/1PPS pulse/s
gives pulses per second for timestamp alignemnt
Input hardware interrupt pin
Output precise timestamp events and sunc signals from other sensors
Syncrhonize hardware from asynchronized sensors

Barometer pressure Pa
converted to altitude in m
Input raw pressure reading, temp
Output altitude, barometric pressure (Pa) and a timestamp

Pitot/Airspeed sensor (Pa -> airspeed in m/s)
Inputs pitot pressure, static pressure, temp
Outputs calibrated airspeed in and a timestamp
Function to convert the barometer data into a target airspeed
Navigation and Control

